There was a crow, the crow was very thristy, the crow was searching for the water but he was not able to find, after some time of searching water,he found a pot where is some water in that pot, but the pot was very big and water is very less inside the ot so it is very down, because the water is very down inside the pot the crow is not able to get it, he was trying and trying to get the water but his mouth is not able to touch it, after some time he see around the pot, there were so many pieces of rocks present there, he started putting the pieces of rocks inside the pot, and when the crow put the rocks inside the pot the water coming up, and after some time the water comes up and the crow drink the water and fly.